    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Absolutely no scratches or dents\u2014it is just pure perfection. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful new-car smell. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make someone very happy. Come take a look, you definitely won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
