    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional ceramic coating; there are no stone chips, dings, or scratches to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-new' state, featuring pristine leather upholstery, untouched carpets, and fully functional electronics with no wear on the buttons. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a complete, documented service history from the authorized dealership. With low mileage, zero accidents, and a clean title in hand, this car offers a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands perfection. Every seal, surface, and mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets the highest standards of quality.",
      "price": 43900.0,
